"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"麻彌","body":"該怎麼說呢，以不好的方面來說，\n就是沒有跳脫出彩同學的感覺呢","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"ev82-ep5-004","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"千聖","body":"就像小彌說的。\n剛剛那樣，就只是樣子有點奇怪的小彩呢……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"ev82-ep5-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"彩","body":"樣子有點奇怪的我……\n我平常又不會發出這種聲音","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"ev82-ep5-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"千聖","body":"小彩在情緒激動的時候，\n就是這種感覺喔？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"ev82-ep5-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"彩","body":"好過分喔〜！　絕對沒有這種事的啦〜！\n嗚嗚……但是，不像殭屍的話還真是困擾耶","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"ev82-ep5-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"千聖","body":"真是的……\n這次的工作，雖然小彩還是扮演小彩，\n但卻已經死了一次而變成殭屍，要記得這一點才行","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"ev82-ep5-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"彩","body":"就算你這麼說……\n我也沒有變成殭屍過，\n要怎麼知道殭屍的心情呀～","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"odoodo01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"ev82-ep5-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"麻彌","body":"嗯～……既然我們有在玩音樂，\n要不要試著從聲音來思考看看呢？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"ev82-ep5-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"千聖","body":"原來如此，感覺可能不錯呢。\n小彩，能請你再扮演一次嗎？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"ev82-ep5-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"彩","body":"嗚、嗚喔～……咕嚕嚕……\n嗚啊～……啊啊～……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"angry01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"ev82-ep5-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"千聖","body":"感覺跟平常的聲音沒什麼不同呢。\n再把嗓音拉低一點，記住自己不是人類\n這樣試試看如何呢","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"ev82-ep5-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"麻彌","body":"也不是說需要發出死亡的聲音……\n但稍微壓著張開的喉嚨，\n發出低沉的聲音，應該就會滿像的了喔","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"ev82-ep5-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"彩","body":"低沉的聲音、稍微壓住喉嚨的